user.biography: we browse through instagram and feature poems and writings we enjoy reading ✨

user.full_name: B E A U   T A P L I N

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 11, 2021 tagging @beautaplin. May be an image of text that says 'A true friend is someone with a sixth sense, someone who can read the silences between your words, and always knows precisely what to say when you are on the verge of a poor decision, someone who shows up with a bottle of wine and a shoulder to lean on before even you know that is what you need most. Beau Taplin Sixth Sense'.

Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 11, 2021 tagging @thepoetlorraine. May be an image of text that says 'I wish I could say we ended with a bang with a fight like an explosion but in reality we ended with the sound offour four unanswered text messages @synchronicitypoetry'.

node.text:
One moment you're there and the next, you're nothing more than a ghost 👻 ⠀
(cr: @thepoetlorraine)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 11, 2021 tagging @william.bortz. May be an image of text that says 'TODAY, THE SUNRISE LOOKS LIKE IT CAN HOLD ME one day decided to take a step and it hurt less than standing still'.

node.text:
Was there a time in your life when you overcame something that felt impossible?⠀
(cr: @william.bortz)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 10, 2021 tagging @sunflowers.poetry. May be an image of text that says 'today found myself at the market junction of your overthinking there were many things being sold fear. insecurities. worries. bought all your fears and turned them into love and then opened my very own stall where gave the same love free of cost -it it never goes out of stock //sunflowers //sunf'.

node.text:
You can never love "too much"⠀
it won't run out 💓⠀
(cr: @sunflowers.poetry)

node.text:

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 10, 2021 tagging @blakeaudenpoetry. May be an image of text that says 'ALL I REALLY kNOW IS WHATEVER THE COST YOU'RE WORTH IT. -BLAKE AUDEN'.

Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 10, 2021 tagging @talesbygendys. May be an image of text that says 'each time say have let go, your ghost comes to say hello and fall back into his arms without hesitation gendys'.

Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 10, 2021 tagging @lonely.penguin. May be an image of text that says 'only a fool would love you with half a heart. you deserve so much more. lonely penguin'.

node.text:
You deserve the world,⠀
tag someone who needs to read this. 😘⠀
(cr: @lonely.penguin)
